Manor Lords players have found a possible solution to trading post traffic jams - the medieval drive-thru                    </a>
                </p>

                  <p class="strapline">I&#39;ll have two sets of plate armour, some iron ore, and a shipment of wheat with extra grain.</p>



          </div>

